version_description: Full version of traditional as performed by Grateful Dead with a slide added in chorus. There is an awesome lead tab for this on the inimitable JDarks site.

Existing tabs are awesome but incomplete, missing a third chorus and both interludes.  This submission is purely chords for basic rhythm guitar (excludes riffs), but entire song is tabbed (including interludes) to facilitate scrolling.

This version is consistent with other versions, except that it includes the entire studio recorded version of the song, which finishes (after the instrumental) with another bridge, a repeat of verse-4 (Chino), and the final chorus).  This makes it easier for our group to scroll through the song consistently.
This version has a moving bass line, which makes it sound more like the original when playing it solo.
